PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775823075
OL,3,C'Challenging' search continues for
OL,4,Ccapybara missing for more than three
OL,5,Cweeks
OL,7,FThe pair had recently arrived from
OL,8,FJimmy's Farm & Wildlife Park in
OL,9,FSuffolk.
OL,11,FSince then, the team has used
OL,12,Fspecialist tracking dogs, drones and
OL,13,Fcamera traps to try and spot Samba but
OL,14,Fwith no luck so far.
OL,16,FVideo footage of Samba resting on a
OL,17,Fbank of the River Itchen, near
OL,18,FWinchester, was shared two weeks ago
OL,19,Fby a dog walker.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
