OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775823075
OL,3,C'Challenging' search continues for
OL,4,Ccapybara missing for more than three
OL,5,Cweeks
OL,7,FKeepers say the search is
OL,8,F"challenging" due to the size of the
OL,9,Farea and Samba's natural instincts to
OL,10,Fstay hidden.
OL,12,FA statement released by Marwell Zoo
OL,13,Fhas assured people that they're "not
OL,14,Fgiving up" and "remain focused" on
OL,15,Fbringing Samba home.
OL,17,FIt said: "Since our last post, we've
OL,18,Freceived a number of reported
OL,19,Fsightings across the surrounding areas.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775823075
OL,3,C'Challenging' search continues for
OL,4,Ccapybara missing for more than three
OL,5,Cweeks
OL,7,F"We're incredibly grateful to everyone
OL,8,Fwho has taken the time to get in
OL,9,Ftouch. Unfortunately, despite thorough
OL,10,Ffollow-ups on these reports, none have
OL,11,Fresulted in a confirmed sighting of
OL,12,FSamba.
OL,14,F"Our teams remain fully committed and
OL,15,Fcontinue to carry out extensive
OL,16,Fsearches both day and night.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
