FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775823075
OL,3,C'Challenging' search continues for
OL,4,Ccapybara missing for more than three
OL,5,Cweeks
OL,7,F"We are still using specialist
OL,8,Ftracking dogs, thermal drone
OL,9,Ftechnology, and camera traps in key
OL,10,Fareas where Samba is most likely to
OL,11,Ftravel, particularly along waterways
OL,12,Fand dense vegetation."
OL,14,FThe zoo has thanked the public for
OL,15,Ftheir ongoing support as well as staff
OL,16,Ffor "working tirelessly" to help look
OL,17,Ffor the capybara.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
